OL,3,CPolice release CCTV of arson attack on
OL,4,Chome which killed 'precious son'
OL,6,FShocking CCTV footage of what police
OL,7,Fsay was a deadly, deliberate, and
OL,8,Ftargeted arson attack on a home in
OL,9,FWolverhampton has been released,
OL,10,Fshowing the moment the house was
OL,11,Fengulfed in flames.
OL,13,FThe security video clearly shows a
OL,14,Ffigure dressed in black, carrying what
OL,15,Fappears to be a petrol canister, as
OL,16,Fthey make their way up Plascom Road in
OL,17,Fthe East Park area, shortly after 1am
OL,18,Fon June 25.
