OL,4,Chome which killed 'precious son'
OL,6,FThey then begin their attack -
OL,7,Frepeatedly smashing the front window
OL,8,Funtil it falls away, before pouring
OL,9,Fpetrol through the gap and setting it
OL,10,Falight.
OL,12,FThe resulting blaze left one man,
OL,13,Fnamed as 26-year-old Akashdeep Singh,
OL,14,Fdead, while four others were taken to
OL,15,Fhospital - two of them, a 16 year old
OL,16,Fboy and a 52 year old woman, are still
OL,17,Fthere, in a critical but stable
OL,18,Fcondition.
