OL,3,CPolice release CCTV of arson attack on
OL,4,Chome which killed 'precious son'
OL,6,F"What is the motive behind it?" Det
OL,7,FSupt Shaun Edwards, from West Midlands
OL,8,FPolice's homicide investigations unit,
OL,9,Fasked.
OL,11,F"We're trying to understand why this
OL,12,Fhappened.
OL,14,F"Secondly, the person or the people
OL,15,Fresponsible would have planned it.
OL,16,FThere would have been an element of
OL,17,Fplanning in terms of carrying out a
OL,18,Frecce, or buying petrol.
