OL,6,F"Has it been targeted deliberately? Or
OL,7,Fhas it been targeted because they
OL,8,Fthought it was another house?
OL,10,F"They're the kind of things we want
OL,11,Fthe public to come forward for. But
OL,12,Fthis isn't a random attack, that house
OL,13,Fwas targeted by the offenders."
OL,15,FHe said because of the size of the
OL,16,Ffireball which erupted when the petrol
OL,17,Fwas set alight, officers believe the
OL,18,Fperson responsible may well have
OL,19,Fsuffered burn injuries themselves.
