OL,6,FMeaning not only do officers want to
OL,7,Fhear from any witnesses or anyone who
OL,8,Fhas heard anything about the attack,
OL,9,Fbut from anybody who has been anyone
OL,10,Fwith burns in the past two weeks.
OL,12,FAkashdeep's family have also released
OL,13,Fa statement in tribute to the man they
OL,14,Fcalled a "true hero" and "precious
OL,15,Fson".
OL,17,F"He was a kind, helpful, and deeply
OL,18,Freligious person whose loss brings us
OL,19,Fimmense pain that will remain with us
OL,20,Ffor the rest of our lives," they said.
