OL,3,CPolice release CCTV of arson attack on
OL,4,Chome which killed 'precious son'
OL,6,F"A true hero, our precious son, whose
OL,7,Fboundless kindness, infectious
OL,8,Flaughter, and unwavering love filled
OL,9,Four lives with immeasurable joy; his
OL,10,Fmemory will forever be cherished, and
OL,11,Fthe depth of his absence is profoundly
OL,12,Ffelt every single day."
OL,14,FAnybody with any information they
OL,15,Fbelieve may help detectives track down
OL,16,Fthe person or people responsible for
OL,17,Fthe attack, and for the death of
OL,18,FAkashdeep, is being urged to call West
OL,19,FMidlands Police on 101, citing log 218
OL,20,Fof 25 June, or Crimestoppers
OL,21,Fanonymously on 0800 555 111.
